                "invention-title": [
                    "Device for coupling concentrating solar thermoelectric generator with electrolytic bath and method for utilizing solar energy",
                    "一种聚光型太阳能温差发电器耦合电解槽的装置和利用太阳能的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of clean energy, and particularly relates to a device for coupling a concentrating solar thermoelectric generator with an electrolytic bath and a method for utilizing solar energy. According to the device, a light-gathering type transparent shell, a solar energy absorption coating, a thermoelectric power generation sheet, a metal cooling fin and other components are utilized to design and construct a light-gathering type solar thermoelectric power generator, the light-gathering type solar thermoelectric power generator, a switch and an electrolytic bath are connected in series and integrated through a wire, and the device for coupling the light-gathering type solar thermoelectric power generator with the electrolytic bath is obtained. The device can focus sunlight to improve heat-electricity conversion efficiency so as to realize power generation. Electric energy output by the concentrating solar thermoelectric generator is used for green and efficient water electrolysis hydrogen production, and clean energy technologies such as a solar light-heat conversion technology, a heat-electricity conversion technology and a water electrolysis hydrogen production technology are creatively integrated and coupled, so that the problems of electric energy output, storage and utilization in solar thermoelectric power generation are solved; and solar energy can be converted into hydrogen energy with high energy density."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于清洁能源技术领域，具体涉及一种聚光型太阳能温差发电器耦合电解槽的装置和利用太阳能的方法。本发明利用聚光型透明壳体、太阳能吸收涂层、温差发电片和金属散热片等部件，设计和构筑出聚光型太阳能温差发电器，利用导线将聚光型太阳能温差发电器、开关和电解槽串联集成，得到聚光型太阳能温差发电器耦合电解槽的装置，该装置可以聚焦太阳光提升热‑电转化效率实现发电。本发明将聚光型太阳能温差发电器输出的电能用于绿色高效地电解水制氢，创造性地将太阳能光‑热转化技术、热‑电转化技术和电解水制氢技术等清洁能源技术进行集成耦合，解决了太阳能温差发电中电能输出及存储利用的问题，而且能够将太阳能转化为高能量密度的氢能。"
                }
            ]
